{"tid":419131,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【鬥神勇討論區】","createTime":"2017-09-30T08:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T18:10:22.000Z","uid":34337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad49fb80b810434748d792b527c03707df3c1bcd","tid":419131,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T08:11:08.000Z","msg":"Hello又係我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又嚟玩下新私服<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呢個服係琴日開嘅：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.godyong.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.godyong.com%2F&d=UTXkjyLHGTBOWen8WItXvi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1add399d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.godyong.com/</a><br />\n同我第一次介紹嘅神御幾乎一模一樣，係回憶啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n懶人包Q&amp;A：<br />\n<br />\nQ：有咩職玩咖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nA：7職，傳統4職+終極+刺客+槍械，新手建議唔好玩終極，因為比較難升<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ：等級/轉生上限？<br />\nA：依家最高30轉，LV350<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ：技書/武器邊度打？<br />\nA：官網有個List比你睇邊度有得打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ：官網積分買咩好先？<br />\nA：建議先買會盔雙戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ：有無泡點？<br />\nA：有，一個鐘40點<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ：應該沖咩先？<br />\nA：先衝武器傷害，最高+150<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ：有無組織入啊？<br />\nA：有，先加我好友<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎問問題/補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 答到一定答<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd6b87d7476b60d5e89cdd834ef5db6d528e256","tid":419131,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T08:17:17.000Z","msg":"補充：裝都係自己打，可以睇官網list邊度有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b4fc1a6c4427808fda9fc44e2d743fe83f36f4","tid":419131,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a37873664ef134c9c4a1c646a2c19cc0200ca5","tid":419131,"uid":5769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:37:30.000Z","msg":"hi!"},{"pid":"6e4c6e568f0888c1dad7b99c8990472031f82367","tid":419131,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hi!</blockquote><br />\nhello<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1257186741aedb52b8b747047eb4d6a08718673","tid":419131,"uid":12784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40745b5d6c15b2f60f85d82136bbd10e806f8823","tid":419131,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:49:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9d254bc71d22c37237145c74c2f971f7353a3e","tid":419131,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efc1e5fce613398ee57216a4e2c0a5c0404b883","tid":419131,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd157c2d875b8118e19f341f9574251221172b5","tid":419131,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15