/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431f735b1710f3e115442c74871fcffb017d5e5e","tid":419131,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T06:18:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341d473fb7f4a4b8d26b70c6ee6c61b15dc07dc6","tid":419131,"uid":101823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:11:18.000Z","msg":"玩左陣好似麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4098740ce2ce32ed915e075cda5b491806681884","tid":419131,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩左陣好似麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔啱玩就唔好勉強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fe55a6c641547a516ee366aef6ac5ebb91e260","tid":419131,"uid":6367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"輔助技係咪要打王出？"},{"pid":"d4ecc906aa2e6ee99a221804c76e99efb4cf0d78","tid":419131,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:56:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輔助技係咪要打王出？</blockquote><br />\nbuff技？照計你已經學曬，要學嘅都係打交用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a27cc7d52dde6877993038ead741802f4ba2238","tid":419131,"uid":6367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>輔助技係咪要打王出？</blockquote><br />\nbuff技？照計你已經學曬，要學嘅都係打交用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，個D係王技？"},{"pid":"bc22903e5e42750b4401ff528234c9cdf7ab5af3","tid":419131,"uid":116861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:08:15.000Z","msg":"可唔可以介紹下終極+刺客+槍械<br />\n未玩過想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae17b486a7906d376b7a53f0179b9ae8fb8ae60d","tid":419131,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:53:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以介紹下終極+刺客+槍械<br />\n未玩過想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n終極係有曬傳統四職嘅技，所以整體上會勁啲，但要打齊技書就會辛苦啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n刺客同槍械相對比較高攻，多數練嚟殺人，不過唔太熟嘅會覺得幾難玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但如果真係想玩都會有人教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed57277dc20c8d6338ba662db7687bde4c23814d","tid":419131,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>輔助技係咪要打王出？</blockquote><br />\nbuff技？照計你已經學曬，要學嘅都係打交用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，個D係王技？</blockquote><br />\nsorry唔太明你問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你係問技書邊度出定咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}